Title: Recursion Rules for Scattering Amplitudes in Non-Abelian Gauge Theories
Authors: Chanju Kim and V. P. Nair (City College of New York)
Comments: 18 pages, RevTeX, 2 postscript figures, a reference added, minor
  typographical errors corrected
Report-no: CCNY-HEP-96/9
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D55 (1997) 3851-3858
\\
  We present a functional derivation of recursion rules for scattering
amplitudes in a non-Abelian gauge theory in a form valid to arbitrary loop
order. The tree-level and one-loop recursion rules are explicitly displayed.
